{# Anti-AI detection rules - from novel-writer spec #}
Apply these anti-AI detection rules (Tencent Zhuque standard):

**Paragraph structure**:
- 30-50% single-sentence paragraphs
- 50-100 chars per paragraph
- Key info in separate lines

**Banned words**: 弥漫着, 唯一的, 摇摇欲坠, 宛如, 仿佛, 犹如, 直到, 猛地, 话音未落, 不禁, 心中暗想, 顿时, 内心涌起, 不由得, 空气凝固, 皱起眉头

**Replace with**: 有股霉味, 就一点光, 一张旧木桌, 像做梦, 删除, 删除, 叹气, 删除

**Principles**:
- One accurate detail > three stacked details
- Concise narration
- Short sentences (15-25 chars)
- Show dialogue, not tell emotions
- Punctuation varies by mood (…… and ...)

